reviewText: If you are a follower of Jesus Christ then this is not something you want to involve yourself or loved ones in. She is an excellent speaker with a new age teaching...

I just watched this and can't say enough about what an amazing job Christiane Northrup did on this.  I watched it with my teenage daughter, which brought up questions that I may not have other wise had the opportunity to talk with her about.  Great for mothers, daughter, granddaughters.  I guess it could also teach the guys a few things too.
Great author.  Clear, concise and easy to understand.  I recommend this product to women.  Husbands watch it with your wife. It will help you take care of each other.

I enjoyed watching this DVD very much.  I learned more about myself and laughed.  Christiane Northrup's wisdom and knowledge about women and women's health and issues is extremely valuable.  After watching this video, I felt even better about being fortunate enough to have been born a woman.
